DISCLAIMER AND TERMS OF USE

This project is built for audio enthusiasts who value high-quality, lossless 
music playback and prefer to maintain full control over their personal media 
libraries. This project is intended for personal use by individuals who wish to 
manage and stream audio files they legally own.

The software is designed for self-hosted environments (such as NAS, home servers, 
Raspberry Pi, or WSL) and does not provide any media content.

Users are solely responsible for ensuring that they have the legal rights to store, 
stream, and reproduce any audio files used with this software.

This project does not promote, support, or facilitate piracy, copyright infringement, 
or unauthorized distribution of copyrighted material.

By using this software, you agree to comply with all applicable copyright laws and 
regulations in your jurisdiction.

